<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Our Projects - Two Dee Engineering</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #ffffff 50%, #f1f5f9 100%); color: #0f172a; }
        
        .navbar { position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; padding: 20px 40px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); z-index: 1000; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(44,94,46,0.1); }
        .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C5E2E 0%, #800020 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .nav-links a { color: #334155; text-decoration: none; margin-left: 30px; font-weight: 500; transition: color 0.3s; position: relative; }
        .nav-links a:hover { color: #2C5E2E; }
        .nav-links a::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -5px; left: 0; width: 0; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2C5E2E, #800020); transition: width 0.3s; }
        .nav-links a:hover::after { width: 100%; }
        
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 140px 40px 80px; }
        .page-title { text-align: center; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #2C5E2E); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .subtitle { text-align: center; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 60px; font-size: 18px; }
        
        .projects-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 30px; }
        .project-card { background: white; border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: all 0.3s; }
        .project-card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); box-shadow: 0 25px 45px rgba(44,94,46,0.12); }
        .project-image { height: 220px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C5E2E, #800020); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 72px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
        .project-image::after { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: -100%; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent); transition: left 0.5s; }
        .project-card:hover .project-image::after { left: 100%; }
        .project-content { padding: 25px; }
        .project-content h3 { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #0f172a; }
        .project-location { color: #2C5E2E; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 14px; }
        .project-content p { color: #64748b; line-height: 1.5; }
        
        .footer { background: #0f172a; color: white; padding: 60px 40px 30px; margin-top: 60px; text-align: center; }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .projects-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .navbar { padding: 15px 20px; }
            .container { padding: 120px 20px 60px; }
            .page-title { font-size: 32px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">Two Dee Engineering</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/services">Services</a>
            <a href="/projects">Projects</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="page-title">Our Projects</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Delivering excellence across diverse sectors</p>

        <div class="projects-grid">
            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-image">🏙️</div>
                <div class="project-content">
                    <h3>Downtown Commercial Tower</h3>
                    <div class="project-location">📍 Austin, TX | 2023</div>
                    <p>35-story mixed-use tower with innovative structural design reducing steel costs by 18%.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-image">🌊</div>
                <div class="project-content">
                    <h3>Riverwalk Plaza</h3>
                    <div class="project-location">📍 San Antonio, TX | 2023</div>
                    <p>12-acre mixed-use development with comprehensive stormwater management system.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-image">🏥</div>
                <div class="project-content">
                    <h3>Coastal Medical Center</h3>
                    <div class="project-location">📍 San Diego, CA | 2024</div>
                    <p>Seismic-resilient medical facility achieving LEED Gold certification.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Two Dee Engineering Services. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 12px;">Licensed PE: TX-123456 | CA-789101</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
